snippet.title: Is Jen Shah Going to Prison? Assistant Stu Flips on Her in Court
snippet.description:
Curious what's gong on with Real Housewives of Salt Lake City star Jen Shah? This week's episode of #NoFilter with Zack Peter is breaking down the charges against her and why things just got a lot worse: 

- Stuart Smith (Jen's Assistant) just plead Guilty in court; says he lied under oath to protect her 
- What are the charges against Stu? 
- How will this impact Jen? 
- Will they actually face prison time?
